{
  "stem": "2004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They considered themselves that they are victims.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now to the best of my recollection, they were not the victims.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they were victims, they were willing, willing victims.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were not-- they were not at all-- just because one was Austrian, to the best of my knowledge, he was no better than a German.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In many cases, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they were as bad or worse than Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German-- not I myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the group of prisoners, whenever we spotted these, we knew exactly who they were because they were our-- oh, we, we grabbed-- a lot of them were hung right on from the tree.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were executed because these people were brutal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they were-- and a lot of them were dragged into the-- they were taken out and sort of lynched.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of them were-- their throats were slashed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, the anger of the inmates was such against those, those German kapos that were in there that it was indescribable.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, that went on for awhile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, of course, the Americans, as soon as they got things a little organized, they stopped it all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they presumably arrested them to give them fair trials and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in Ebensee, I myself saw many, many of these German in their administration, the prisoners, the ones that-- the brutal ones, they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The soldiers were gone, so we couldn't catch any soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But as far as the-- we didn't even, even see the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They must have escaped, I think, the night before, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And had the Germans, the kapos known about it, they would've probably gone along with them, or they would have escaped themselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they never knew about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
